      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and let me tell you, it's been a total joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014very dependable, clean, and still looks great on the road! It\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for a reliable ride that's ready to go, this is definitely the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions or come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) optimized for the purist. This chassis retains the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that has been recently serviced for optimal timing advance. Power is delivered via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. Significant preventative measures have been completed, including rear subframe reinforcement and the replacement of rear trailing arm bushings (RTABs) to maintain toe stability under load. The suspension geometry is currently supported by a set of adjustable coilovers, providing sharpened turn-in response. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical synchronization and drivetrain rigidity remain excellent. This is a robust, driver-spec example ready for spirited apex-hunting.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Used car for sale. Good condition. Mechanically sound. Minimal exterior wear. Clean title. Service records available.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a well-maintained example of its model, offering a blend of reliability and comfort. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch consistent with regular use. The alloy wheels are free of major curb rash and are wrapped in tires with plenty of tread remaining. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the leather seats show only light wear on the driver's side bolster, and all interior trim pieces are secure. Every feature, including the touchscreen infotainment, heated seats, and sunroof, is fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in strong health with a documented service history. Recent maintenance includes a cooling system flush and a new battery. It drives straight, brakes firmly, and the engine delivers smooth power without any hesitation. This is a dependable, honest car ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical reliability and sophisticated design. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for performance and safety. Featuring a clean interior and a well-preserved exterior finish, it offers an exceptional balance of value and prestige. We invite serious inquiries to experience the refined driving dynamics of this distinguished automobile.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car. Honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive and has served me incredibly well. It\u2019s in really solid shape and is ready to hit the road with a new owner! If you're looking for a reliable, comfy ride for your daily commutes or weekend trips, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have. Feel free to shoot me a message if you have any questions or want to come see it in person!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) Coupe, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system that has been professionally overhauled for optimal cam timing. Power is delivered via a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to an M-Variable Differential Lock, ensuring maximum traction through the corners. The chassis has been proactively addressed with rear subframe reinforcement plates to mitigate common floor pan fatigue. While the aesthetic condition is consistent with a well-loved 'good' tier example, the mechanical vitals are superb, featuring recent rod bearing replacement and a refreshed cooling system. This is a high-revving, analog machine tuned for the discerning pilot who prioritizes drivetrain integrity and tactile feedback.",
      "price": 32500.0,
